Create an interactive credit card details form with real-time card preview and validation.

## **Layout Structure:**
- Use a two-column grid layout: 30% for card display, 70% for form
- Left section: Display two overlapping credit cards (front and back)
- Right section: Input form with validation and completed state
- Use semantic HTML5 with `<main>`, `<section>`, and proper labels

## **Credit Card Display (Left Section):**
- **Front Card:** 
  - Purple gradient background (images/bg-card-front.png)
  - Display: Card number (formatted in groups of 4), cardholder name, expiry date (MM/YY)
  - White card logo (images/card-logo.svg)
  - Position: Upper card, slightly offset to left
- **Back Card:**
  - Light grey background (images/bg-card-back.png)
  - Display: CVC number
  - Position: Lower card, slightly offset to right
- Cards should overlap with 10px gap between them

## **Input Form (Right Section):**
**Default Form State:**
- **Cardholder Name field:** Text input, placeholder "e.g. Jane Appleseed"
- **Card Number field:** Text input, maxlength 19, placeholder "e.g. 1234 5678 9123 0000"
- **Expiry Date:** Two separate inputs in flex container
  - Month input: maxlength 2, placeholder "MM", pattern to reject letters
  - Year input: maxlength 2, placeholder "YY"
- **CVC field:** Text input, maxlength 3, placeholder "e.g. 123"
- **Confirm button:** Dark violet background, white text, rounded corners

**Completed State:**
- Success icon (images/icon-complete.svg)
- "Thank you!" title (28px, uppercase, letter-spacing 0.15em)
- "We've added your card details" description (18px)
- "Continue" button to reset form

## **Real-time Updates:**
- As user types in name field → Update card name display
- As user types card number → Format with spaces every 4 digits, update card display
- As user types expiry → Update month/year displays on card
- As user types CVC → Update CVC display on back card

## **Validation Logic:**
- **Name:** Cannot be blank, must match name pattern (letters, spaces, hyphens)
- **Card Number:** Must be 16 digits, format "XXXX XXXX XXXX XXXX", numbers only
- **Month:** Must be 01-12, numbers only
- **Year:** Must be 2 digits, not outdated (current year check)
- **CVC:** Must be 3 digits, numbers only
- Show error messages below each field with red text

## **Styling Requirements:**
**CSS Variables:**
- `--linearGradientBorder`: Purple to violet gradient for focus states
- `--redError`: Red for validation errors
- `--white`, `--lightGrayishViolet`, `--darkGrayishViolet`, `--veryDarkViolet`
- `--fs-large`: 22.5px, `--fs-medium`: 16px
- Font: Space Grotesk, weight 500

**Interactive States:**
- **Focus:** Double border with gradient background
- **Error:** 2px solid red border
- **Valid:** 2px solid gray border
- **Hover states** on buttons

**Responsive Design:**
- **Desktop (>1150px):** Side-by-side layout, cards 375x195px, form 420px wide
- **Tablet (800-1150px):** Adjust card sizes to 290x170px, reposition
- **Mobile (<800px):** Stack layout, cards 290x150px, form 90% width, centered

## **JavaScript Functionality:**
- Event listeners for focusin, focusout, and input events
- Input validity array tracking form state
- Real-time card updates as user types
- Form submission: Check all inputs valid, show completed state
- Continue button: Reset form, clear inputs, show default form
- Auto-format card number with spaces
- Prevent non-numeric input for number fields

## **Assets Required:**
- `images/bg-main-desktop.png` - Desktop background
- `images/bg-main-mobile.png` - Mobile background  
- `images/bg-card-front.png` - Front card background
- `images/bg-card-back.png` - Back card background
- `images/card-logo.svg` - Card logo
- `images/icon-complete.svg` - Success icon
- `images/favicon-32x32.png` - Favicon

## **Technical Specifications:**
- Use CSS Grid for main layout
- CSS custom properties for theming
- Flexbox for card layouts and form structure
- Transform positioning for overlapping cards
- Background-clip technique for gradient borders
- Smooth transitions between form states

This creates a fully functional, responsive interactive card details form with real-time preview, comprehensive validation, and modern design matching Frontend Mentor specifications.
